casebody.data:
Eileen L. KELLY, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
FLINT BOARD OF EDUCATION, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 159297
COA: 345258 Supreme Court of Michigan. July 29, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the February 15, 2019 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court.
